EI Annexure Converter + Renderer — Final Consolidated Red Flags

Baseline verified working: Composition Excel parsing, per-component daily 
exposure math (mg/dose × ppm ÷ 1000), Total row summation, PDE reference 
values (ICH Q3D R2), 30% threshold row, Option 1 compliance verdict, 
route inference (oral / parenteral / subcutaneous), warning-first validation.

All red flags below are ANNEXURE CONVERTOR + RENDERER bugs that cause 
extraction errors, mapping failures, unit conversion errors, sequential 
numbering failures, or duplication. Fix product-agnostic. Do not regress 
working paths.

