GLOBAL RULES (preserve prior fixes)
═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

- Warning-first validation. Never hard-block on missing data.
- Placeholder "Not provided." in empty DOCX sections. No "manual review" 
  language in DOCX body.
- Multi-page annexure extraction: process ALL pages of every PDF.
- BQL / ND / <LOQ handling: use LOD/LOQ as worst-case value, NEVER 0.0.
- 30% PDE threshold rule for compliance verdict (Option 1 or Option 2b).
- Sequential Annexure 1..N numbering.
- Cluster before mapping (annexure_identity_clustering.py).
- Product-agnostic. All rules apply to any product without code changes.
